    "In this paper, the threshold was set to be 0.5.",
    "A limitation of the single-linkage method is its requirement to specify the number of clusters, which can be difficult without prior knowledge.",
    "To mitigate this, we also experimented with DB-SCAN (Ester et al., 1996), a density-based clustering method that adjusts the number of clusters dynamically based on the density of sentence embeddings.",
